content.rendered:
Directed by Manish Vatssalya. Saurabh Choudhary

Written by Shahzad Ahmed. Saurabh Choudhary. Varadraj Swami. Varadraj Swami

Cast Neil Nitin Mukesh (Rudra Pratap Singh Chauhan). Tina Desai (Aditi Singh (as Tena Desae)). Manish Vatssalya (Shankar (as Manish Vatsalya)). Govind Namdeo (Prasadilal Yadav (as Govind Namdev)). Ashwini Kalsekar (Kanchan devi). Murali Sharma (Sub Insp. Dulare (as Murli Sharma)). Shubhangi Gokhale (Imarti Devi). Scarlett Mellish Wilson (Item Girl). Pankaj Jha (Tripathi). Nisa Deys (Item Girl). Pooja Welling(Pooja Kumari) . Arya Babbar (Honey Singh). Sumit Choudhary (Pandey).Kumar Gautam. Yana Gupta (Special appearance in the song ‘Joganiya’). Anjali Guta (Nurse). Pragya (Inspector anjana (as Pragya Maheshwari)). Samar (Pandhari). Sharat Saxena (DGP N K Sharma).Anuj Sharma. Amit Singh (Constable (credit only)). Manmeet Singh (P.A. to C.M.). Naushaad Abbas (Fighter (uncredited))

Language Hindi

Producers Aparna Hoshing. Aparana S Hosing

Production Rash Production
